==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dude
<hw>Dude</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of dandy;
especially, one characterized by an ultrafashionable style of dress and
other affectations.</def> <mark>[Recent]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The social <qex>dude</qex> who affects English dress and English
drawl.</q> <rj><qau>The American.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dudeen</ent>⟦br⟧
